description: A timeless and elegant art deco design, inspired by Lincrusta's historic archives from the 1920s.

A beautifully bohemian nod to the traditional organics theme, our statement-making Tropical Leaf features a deep texture that works equally well with bright, block colors or softer, more natural hues.
Inspired by tropical flora in Kew Gardens' iconic Victorian glasshouses, this striking yet simple print has a delicate, multi-layered structure that takes its cue from nature.
